author: Minecraft
description:
Minecraft LIVE – The Deep Dig after-show saw both developers and guests get their hands on a bunch of new features from both The Copper Age AND Mounts of Mayhem.  

Mogswamp and Shubble inspired us with copper-inspired builds. Tubbo, Agnes, and Linda explored the ocean with their nautilus mounts. And – what better way to end a show than with a grand mount-themed triathalon thing? There’s probably no better way!

author: Minecraft
description:
Minecraft LIVE revealed a sneak peek of Minecraft's next game drop: MOUNTS OF MAYHEM, as well as a first look at some of upcoming features! Discover the spear, a new weapon that will change how you approach combat encounters forever, and the nautilus: an underwater, rideable mob that will make deep sea exploration a little less daunting. We also unveil the mounted drowned who will make sure your expeditions aren’t too relaxing! 

New features coming to testing soon!
